<title>Family Research Council FAQ</title>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000">

<center><h2>Family Research Council FAQ (Frequently Asked 
Questions)</h2></center>

<ol><h4>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq1.html">Why does FRC exist and 
what do they stand for?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq2.html">What does FRC think about 
AIDS funding?</a>

