http://www.atr.org:80/discovery/macavoy.html 204.71.237.87 19970209115015 text/html 28809
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 11:50:52 GMT
