<TITLE>EVGUENI VOLK -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>EVGUENI VOLK</H3>
<B>MOSCOW OFFICE COORDINATOR</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/volk.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
A native of Russia, Volk is an international security and economics expert who heads Heritage's Moscow Office. He serves as a liaison between Heritage and the Russian reformers, as their nation struggles to become a more democratic, free-market society. Volk is a former deputy director for the Russian Institute for Strategic Studies and  previously was Advisor to the Committee on Defense and Security Issues for the Supreme Soviet of the Russian Federation.   Volk  also  has   served  as  Soviet  Ministry of Foreign Affairs. He is a graduate of the Moscow State Institute of International Relations.

<BR><HR WIDTH="30%"><BR><CENTER><A HREF="/heritage/hbut.map"><IMG SRC="/heritage/hbut.gif" ISMAP BORDER=0></A></CENTER></BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
