<TITLE> January 1996 What's New Index -- Town Hall</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<P>




<CENTER><IMG SRC="/townhall/whats_new/tnew.gif" WIDTH=425 HEIGHT=100
 BORDER=0 LOWSRC="/townhall/whats_new/tnewl.jpeg">
<P>
</center>
<h2>March's Contents</h2>
<b>3/29/96</b>
<ul>
<li><a href="/nationalreview/08apr96/feature.html">Competition v. Discrimination</a> is the feature article in the latest <i>National Review</i>.
<li>Are you wondering about Big Labor's <i>real</i> agenda? Then <a href="mailto:rstikes@sbsc.org">request</a> (rstikes@sbsc.org) the FREE fax service from <a href="/sbsc/">Small Business Survival Committee</a> called <b>Labor Watch</b>.
<li>Edwin J. Feulner, Jr., president of <a href="/heritage/">The Heritage Foundation</a> discusses <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef17.html">Lower Education</a> in this week's op-ed.
