<P>
<b>Updated 10/31/95</b><br>
<ul>
<li>Don't miss this week's issue of <a href="/wash_times/">The Washington Times</a> National Weekly Edition!
<li>More on <a href="/nationalreview/daily/nr1030.html">Powell</a> from the Washington Daily News of National Review.
<li>New <a href="/pff/new.html">additions</a> from the Progress and Freedom Foundation on the budget, welfare, and more!
<li><a href="/empower/pr1027.html">Jack Kemp</a> urges Budget Conference Committee to strengthen reconciliation.
<li><a href="/pff/congtest/ct101795.html">Arianna Huffington</a> gives testimony on Americorps. 
</ul>
<b>Updated 10/30/95</b><br>
<ul>
<li>William Bennett of Empower American and Sen. Joseph Lieberman of CT denounce lurid <a href="/empower/pr1025.html">daytime talk</a> show content.
<li>"End the <a href="/pff/project/tl-1019.html">FDA</a> Monopoly"...from the Progress and Freedom Foundation.
<li>Discover the <a href="/sbsc/pubs.html">publications</a> of the Small Business Survival Committee.
<li>"For the <a href="/nationalreview/06nov95/fortherec.htm">Record</a>" from National Review.
</ul>
