<li>Town Hall's <a href="/townhall/spotlights/10-23-95/welcome.html#Misc">Weekly Spotlight</a> focuses on the Million Man March and issues such as affirmative action and welfare. <a href="/townhall/spotlights/10-23-95/i-friday.html">Today</a> black business leaders discuss affirmative action.
