<b>Updated 9/27/95</b><br>
<ul>
<li>The Leadership Institute has trained thousands of young conservatives to be successful in politics. The <a href="/lead-inst/sc-yl.html">Youth Leadership School</a>  is traveling to Tennessee, Florida, Colorado, California, and Washington DC this fall to train you!
