<P><B>Chapter 17 
</B></P>
<P><B><a href="chpt17.html">MAKING THE WORLD SAFE FOR AMERICA</a>&#160; &#160; <a href="/heritage/issues96/pdf/chap_17.pdf"><b>.pdf version</b></a>
</B></P>
<P><B><i>&#160;&#160By <a href="/heritage/staff/moore.html">Thomas Moore</a>, <a href="/heritage/staff/cohen.htm">Ariel Cohen</a>, <a href="/heritage/staff/hillen.html">John Hillen</a>, <a href="/heritage/staff/sweeney.htm">John Sweeney</a>, <a href="/heritage/staff/phillips.htm">James Phillips</a>, and <a href="/heritage/staff/przystup.htm">James Przystup</a> </i> 

