<B>Chapter 18 
</B></P>
<P><B><a href="chpt18.html">TRADE AND DEVELOPMENT</a>&#160; &#160; <a href="/heritage/issues96/pdf/chap_18.pdf"><b>.pdf version</b></a> 
</B></P>
<P><B><i>&#160;&#160By <a href="/heritage/staff/johnson.htm">Bryan Johnson</a>, <a href="/heritage/staff/oquinn.htm">Robert O'Quinn</a>, <a href="/heritage/staff/sweeney.htm">John Sweeney</a>               
</i></B></P>
