 <DD><a href="mailto:moebiusw@heritage.org">Wanda Moebius</a>,
 <DD><I>Acting Speakers Bureau Coordinator</I>
 <DD>The Heritage Foundation
 <DD>214 Massachusetts Ave., N.E.
 <DD>Washington, D.C.  20002
 <DD>(202) 675-1761
</DL>
