http://www.atr.org:80/heritage/p_review/spring95/tolerth.html 204.71.237.87 19970209121322 text/html 24862
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 12:14:06 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:29:28 GMT
Content-length: 24678
